ActAeronautics Act
SubjectRegulations Amending the Designated Provisions Regulations and the Identity Screening Regulations
PrecisRegulations Amending the DESIGNATED PROVISIONS REGULATIONS and the IDENTITY SCREENING REGULATIONS, in order to codify Interim Order No. 3 Respecting Identity Screening and enable Canada to continue to fulfill its international and departmental responsibility to establish and implement regulations to safeguard aviation operations against acts of unlawful interference.
